Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.39,0:00:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有神田同學的信哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.48,0:00:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有兩封
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.48,0:00:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.86,0:00:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎…怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.44,0:00:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}青山同學 原來你一直都是戴隱形眼鏡的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.62,0:00:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我一不小心就以這幅打扮…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.58,0:00:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神田你不要盯著看啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼只有我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.33,0:00:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}戴眼鏡的七海也好可愛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.67,0:00:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}快讓我好好看看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.09,0:00:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要 學姐 快住手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.38,0:00:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an8}都是女孩子 沒關係的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.01,0:00:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}於是 那封信呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.26,0:00:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.42,0:00:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an9}不可以 有男生在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:36.09,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fad(450,0)\frz344.6\fs20\pos(190,342)}「一起製作遊戲吧」評選委員
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.43,0:00:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那接下來的是回房裡？還是去浴室？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.01,0:00:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哪邊都不行的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.01,0:00:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道了 那就去外面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.77,0:00:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人生是需要一些驚喜的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.44,0:00:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}No surprise, no life啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.27,0:00:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.28,0:00:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}通過初選了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讓我31號去面試
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.03,0:00:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的嗎?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.95,0:00:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太好了呢 學弟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.32,0:00:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太好了呢 七海！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.82,0:00:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太好了呢 空太
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.24,0:01:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.37,0:01:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼 另一封呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.76,0:01:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\1a&H1C&\shad0\bord0\fn華康竹風體W4\c&HA6BBC4&\pos(640,394.6)\frz359.8}教我戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.63,0:01:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.93,0:01:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你知道什麼是戀愛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.75,0:01:46.96,NCOP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}一回目　まぐれで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.75,0:01:46.96,NCOP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}第一次邂逅 若是偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,0:01:50.21,NCOP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}二回目ってどうだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,0:01:50.21,NCOP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}那麼第二次 又是如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.63,0:01:53.92,NCOP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}偶然じゃないよね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.63,0:01:53.92,NCOP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}果然並非偶然吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.01,0:01:57.63,NCOP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}三回 目が合うのは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.01,0:01:57.63,NCOP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}第三次 彼此注視之時
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.13,0:02:01.01,NCOP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}変わった人だと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.13,0:02:01.01,NCOP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}真是個怪人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.26,0:02:04.56,NCOP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}割とみんな言うけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.26,0:02:04.56,NCOP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}大家意外的異口同聲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.97,0:02:07.89,NCOP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}気になったことは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.97,0:02:07.89,NCOP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}但這就是我在意他的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.10,0:02:11.77,NCOP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}違うんだ そこじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.10,0:02:11.77,NCOP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}不對啦 才不是那裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.27,0:02:15.69,NCOP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}君は多分　純粋で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.27,0:02:15.69,NCOP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}你恐怕十分的純粹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.86,0:02:18.28,NCOP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}純粋を曲げず
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.86,0:02:18.28,NCOP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}不願扭曲自身的純粹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.49,0:02:25.62,NCOP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}だから小さな日常にさえ立ち向かって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.49,0:02:25.62,NCOP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}所以就連瑣碎的日常 你也依然毫不退步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.62,0:02:29.42,NCOP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}夢を持ってきた言葉じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.62,0:02:29.42,NCOP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}那些帶來夢想的話語
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.58,0:02:32.75,NCOP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}足りない夢の在り処
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.58,0:02:32.75,NCOP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}描繪夢想缺失的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.75,0:02:36.09,NCOP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}きっとこんな風に始まる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.75,0:02:36.09,NCOP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}一定就像是這樣開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.34,0:02:39.63,NCOP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}新しいトキメキ世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.34,0:02:39.63,NCOP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}嶄新而又精彩的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.84,0:02:43.18,NCOP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}夢を持ってきた言葉を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.84,0:02:43.18,NCOP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}就把那些帶來夢想的話語
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.35,0:02:46.89,NCOP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}知らない振りしてゆこう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.35,0:02:46.89,NCOP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}拋於身後裝作不聞不知吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.89,0:02:51.23,NCOP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}トキメキと夢の在り処
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.89,0:02:51.23,NCOP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}出發前往精彩夢境的所在
