Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就這麼點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.30,0:06:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要幫忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}修業篇開幕啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\bord0\shad0\fn華康竹風體W4\c&H497984&\pos(916.8,314.6)}學\N弟\N 修\N業\N篇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.48,0:06:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呃…基於這樣的系統
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.10,0:06:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我希望不僅僅是讓核心玩家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.65,0:06:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也能讓一般玩家樂在其中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.24,0:06:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}20分53秒 太長了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我試著參考了一下網路上藤沢和希獲獎時的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.04,0:06:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要說明地讓人聽得出起承轉合啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感覺和平時的學弟一點都不像 好無趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}敬語也有很多奇怪的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}參雜了過多的要素 讓人聽不懂你最想表明的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.27,0:07:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神田同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今晚 我再重新改一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明天也拜託各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他是認真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.32,0:07:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}加油 順利的話七海會親你一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}才不會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只是親臉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.91,0:07:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這不是親在哪裡的問題啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}觀念要簡明有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 要簡明扼要…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 要清爽…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}椎名 你跑來別人的房間做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.18,0:07:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我在設計角色中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.44,0:07:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那…為什麼在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感覺在這裡做的話 就能明白什麼是戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.07,0:07:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不能在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.07,0:07:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呃 不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不能在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.12,0:08:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被青山發現的話又會生氣的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.08,0:08:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那我就待在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}空太一開口說話就是七海
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.38,0:08:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}算了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.16,0:08:43.12,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\1c&H111111\t(1615,3700,\1c&H111133)\fs18\frz126\pos(761,481)}注意身體
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}然後 太陽升起 又再度落下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}關於報告上的修改 參考著大家的意見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.30,0:08:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不斷地修改著 不斷地練習著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.43,0:08:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在重復了大約10次左右的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我迎來了決戰之日的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.10,0:09:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.94,0:09:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}空太
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.82,0:09:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}昨天去的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.49,0:09:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}和誰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}查過了 也問了人 走了很久
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}難道你…一個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.25,0:09:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 明明今天也是決定你能否連載的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.38,0:09:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一路順風
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.55,0:09:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.49,0:10:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼 神田空太先生 請開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請…請多關照！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.09,0:10:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}藤沢和希
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在正式開始之前 我可以問一個問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.72,0:10:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你認為要成為遊戲製作者應該要怎麼做才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.44,0:10:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這… 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不說點什麼的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.49,0:10:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說點什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.95,0:10:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個… 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不行了 腦子裡一片空白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.89,0:11:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是這樣想的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.27,0:11:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}接下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.56,0:11:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.32,0:11:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喲 這不是神田家的小哥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.73,0:11:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼這身打扮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.99,0:11:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這不是明擺著的嗎 約會？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.16,0:11:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂喂 怎麼了 小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.58,0:11:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神田空太先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.17,0:11:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神田先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.63,0:11:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神田先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.38,0:11:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}非常遺憾 您與本次的甄選無緣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.91,0:12:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}空太
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.67,0:12:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.42,0:12:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.22,0:12:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}連載的事怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.88,0:12:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}決定了 從十一月號
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣啊 恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.27,0:12:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.81,0:12:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼不趕快畫的話可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}快走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.60,0:12:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}空太
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.77,0:12:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別待在這裡了 快去畫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.98,0:12:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在先別靠近我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.99,0:12:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.11,0:12:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}椎名
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}否則的話 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}待在這裡是不會向前邁進的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.04,0:12:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我… 會對你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.73,0:13:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣啊 是安慰獎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}本身就不是件容易的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.57,0:13:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}空太也有心理準備的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.82,0:13:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}話雖如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.53,0:13:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}很在意嗎 七海 親~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}才不會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.37,0:13:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好 青山同學的歡迎會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an8}我贊成 不愧是仁 好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等一下 為什麼會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}照現在這個情況 也只能是今天了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.59,0:13:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}既然決定好了 那就事不宜遲啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.26,0:13:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我有些早就準備好的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.68,0:13:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an8}好 全員六點集合
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.14,0:13:59.10,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\an5\bord0\1c&H111111\be1\fs25\frz13.34\move(777,336,716,281)\t(\fs30)}「一起製作遊戲吧」\N通過初審的相關指南
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\fn華康竹風體W4\b1\bord0\shad0\c&H06050D&\pos(734.4,594.6)}寶箱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.03,0:14:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}學弟！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.79,0:14:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好啊 學弟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這一天終於到來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全人類都期待著的約定之日
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}吶吶 學弟覺得哪款好？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.80,0:14:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這...這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}內衣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.05,0:14:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是 是泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.34,0:14:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼對於內衣和泳衣的反應相差這麼遠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.47,0:14:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是個謎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.39,0:14:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別一個人在那陷入沉思了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}往別人房間裡扔這麼多泳衣你想做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.15,0:14:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想舉辦七海的游泳歡迎大會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.11,0:14:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來 讓我們出發吧 學弟！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我和七海和真白和我的泳裝姿態在等著你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.37,0:14:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你把自己的名字說了兩遍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.33,0:14:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再說這種時間泳池還營業嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.37,0:14:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去學校裡不就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.54,0:15:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂 你不會是想潛入學校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.54,0:15:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒問題 仁他…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}從千尋那得到許可了 沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.92,0:15:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等一下 學長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.47,0:15:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我對於歡迎會什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.43,0:15:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來的正好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.72,0:15:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}青山同學也來選件喜歡的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.26,0:15:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要不我來幫你選吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.27,0:15:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這到底是怎麼一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.39,0:15:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要舉辦七海的游泳歡迎大會嘛~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.69,0:15:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}七海要選哪件？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.98,0:15:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}學弟說這件不錯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.44,0:15:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我沒說過啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.48,0:15:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an8}神田同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可別搞錯戰鬥的對像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.15,0:15:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}敵人是這個宇宙人！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}果然還是吊帶式吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.03,0:15:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an8}三鷹學長！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.07,0:15:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}仁學長！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.41,0:15:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們兩個快給我適可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.53,0:15:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我還沒說我要去啊 而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.21,0:15:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不會去泳池的 快點收拾起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.88,0:15:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎.... 去嘛 一起去嘛 七海 學弟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.63,0:15:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不行 再說明天起就開學了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.43,0:15:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒錯 就是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.01,0:15:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不穿一回泳裝暑假就不能算結束 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:15:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是這樣 就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.60,0:16:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.86,0:16:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去吧 青山游泳歡迎大會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.03,0:16:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}汪洋大海在召喚著我~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.12,0:16:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}先做下準備運動比較好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.70,0:16:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}青山和椎名呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.21,0:16:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}差不多該換完衣服了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.71,0:16:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎...麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.26,0:16:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太普通了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我可沒有問三鷹學長！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.14,0:16:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼都別說！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.31,0:16:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我覺得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.02,0:16:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真 真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是又不像上井草學姐的那麼大膽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.07,0:16:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒辦法 對我來說這已經是極限了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.90,0:16:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這種我還是第一次穿 要是很奇怪的話該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.08,0:17:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 真的挺適合的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}變成關西腔了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}空太
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.21,0:17:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.26,0:17:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.51,0:17:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}空太是笨蛋 明明誇了七海
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.64,0:17:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是是 很適合
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.14,0:17:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.48,0:17:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.91,0:17:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.08,0:17:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}吃我一招
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.00,0:17:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}浮板飛鏢！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.25,0:17:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神 神田同學？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.09,0:17:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神田同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:18:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看我的！~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.77,0:18:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}走吧 青山同學 一起跑起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.02,0:18:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等我一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.49,0:18:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}必殺！尼亞加拉加拉盆子瀑布！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.95,0:18:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}波動雨試射！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.50,0:18:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}笨蛋 要遮的話 就先遮好自己的胸部啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.12,0:18:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}解不開
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.92,0:18:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這裡已經被學弟所占領了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.84,0:18:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an8}還給我 還給我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.17,0:18:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an8}變態！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.55,0:18:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an8}真是倒楣啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.51,0:18:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}提到游泳大會的話 果然少不了走光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.39,0:18:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an8}沒走光的話 可是一點都不幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.01,0:18:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}特地把這個帶過來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.01,0:18:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an8}來來 學弟也快吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.31,0:18:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}櫻花莊的歡迎會少不了火鍋不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.39,0:18:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咖哩味
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.19,0:18:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.23,0:18:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂 你們 在這裡做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.15,0:18:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.94,0:18:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好快！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.07,0:18:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三鷹學長 你不是說拿到許可了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.28,0:19:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}學校怎麼可能會給這種許可嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.99,0:19:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}果然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.24,0:19:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}總之先藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.37,0:19:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}換衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.37,0:19:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂 跑哪去了 給我出來！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們這群泳池小偷！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.62,0:19:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啪嗒啪嗒鬧得那麼吵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.42,0:19:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這…這是什麼情況啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別亂動 神田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.26,0:19:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}噓 安靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.55,0:19:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}絕對別轉過來啊 絕對哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.22,0:19:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別動啊 椎名
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}新的護身符 刺繡比之前的好看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.23,0:19:36.32,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\c&H303839&\fn華康中特圓體\fs22\pos(376,177)}安\N產\N祈\N願
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.16,0:19:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是現在 跑起來！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.05,0:20:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我還以為你會更消沉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.22,0:20:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我確實很消沉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.64,0:20:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哇 真美
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.73,0:20:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}煙火？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}椎名？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.71,0:20:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不可以止步不前哦 空太
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.59,0:20:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.93,0:20:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個大叔好嚇人的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.80,0:20:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們這些小鬼是櫻花莊的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.31,0:20:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}擅自在那裡謳歌青春 我絕不會饒過你們的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.00,0:21:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不妙 總覺得越來越有趣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.71,0:21:23.22,NCED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\an9\blur2}・過ぎるだけの  時間じゃ悔しい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.71,0:21:23.22,NCED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\an9\blur2\pos(819,20)}一味流逝的時光 徒增懊悔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.63,0:21:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哭出來也沒關係哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.84,0:21:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不會哭的 我又不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.67,0:21:25.80,NCED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\an9\blur2}・刻まなくちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.67,0:21:25.80,NCED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\an9\blur2\pos(1062,20)}唯有銘記於心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.72,0:21:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼嘛 難得人家好心安慰你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.59,0:21:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這感覺太棒了啊 認真地投入於一件事中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.18,0:21:32.06,NCED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\an9\blur2}・「此処にいる」と心が叫ぶ瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.18,0:21:32.06,NCED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\an9\blur2\pos(812,20)}「我就在這裡」 內心如此吶喊的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.93,0:21:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}回來的時候 聽椎名說連載已經決定了的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.31,0:21:34.60,NCED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\an9\blur2}I'm dreaming
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.81,0:21:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感覺就好像自己被否定了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.48,0:21:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}心裡充滿著挫敗感
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.73,0:21:41.23,NCED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\an9\blur2}・迷いながら  涙を飲み込んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.73,0:21:41.23,NCED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\an9\blur2\pos(843,20)}不斷迷茫著 逞強噙住眼角淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.52,0:21:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}正因為是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.98,0:21:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以無法從那後悔和不甘心的感覺之中逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.73,0:21:47.36,NCED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\an9\blur2}・不器用だね　夢も遠回り
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.73,0:21:47.36,NCED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\an9\blur2\pos(905,20)}真是笨拙呢 連夢想都不斷繞道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.07,0:21:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但也因為如此 答案才會如此明瞭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.15,0:21:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只能放手去做了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.40,0:21:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為了回應這份心情 只能放手去做了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.74,0:21:53.37,NCED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\an9\blur2}・大空を見上げ　何も見えず
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.74,0:21:53.37,NCED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\an9\blur2\pos(876,20)}仰望這片廣闊的天空 卻無法確認一物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.57,0:21:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}失敗了也好 被否定也好 都只能做下去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.20,0:21:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這麼一想後 就變得興奮起來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.66,0:22:01.67,NCED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\an9\blur2}・胸が痛むわけ考えていた
